<tr><td>**Savings / Debt Reduction (20%)**</td><td>Emergency fund, retirement contributions, brokerage investing, extra student loan or credit-card payments, sinking funds for future goals</td><td>This bucket builds resilience, reduces leverage, and creates future wealth</td></tr>
